 />\n成熟期走左去打完全體<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家兩隻超究極體又就死<br />\n唔想再升過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎200繁</blockquote><br />\n我就係岩岩兩隻究極體死左 兩個只係差一歲左右 搞到又冇得帶升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩辦法可以令佢地既歲數相差2-3歲</blockquote><br />\n同埋其實幾個stat打海龍先比較好 而家兩隻完全體打都仲好</blockquote><br />\n如果成長期有千幾攻防就可以老屈海龍<br />\n速同智我到宜家都唔知有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我而家一隻完全體一隻成熟體 兩隻都有過千攻防 但係都打得好吃力 我有冇打錯地方 地點係唔係mod3.0入面既海龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請善用加stat 既技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我兩隻成長期打到7-8k 先進成熟期<br />\n之後剩係係訓練場升到究極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb0bcac470fa9f18f3af174f53e83865546430a","tid":201100,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n因為升到個隻怪可以比你能力既上限<br />\n打海龍好似可以2500左右<br />\n但唔知暴龍師技能會唔會影響個上限</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩升滿左暴龍師技能 個stat既上限會升<br />\n 但係唔知係唔係隻究極體d stat廢 靠佢一隻喺海角打好吃力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係成長期打海龍仲可以多過2k5<br />\n成熟期走左去打完全體<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家兩隻超究極體又就死<br />\n唔想再升過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎200繁</blockquote><br />\n我就係岩岩兩隻究極體死左 兩個只係差一歲左右 搞